These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
Hobby: puzzles, reading, dancing, writing
Movie-Genre: fantasy, crime, zombie, western
Birthday: march, august, june, july
1. Birthday:june is on the left of Movie-Genre:crime##1
2. Birthday:july == Movie-Genre:fantasy##1
3. Hobby:dancing is on the far left##1
4. Hobby:puzzles is on the far right##1
5. Movie-Genre:crime is between Birthday:june and Hobby:reading##2
6. Birthday:august == Movie-Genre:zombie##1
7. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the right of Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby        | dancing | writing  | reading | puzzles  |
| Movie-Genre         | western    | crime  | fantasy       | zombie     |
| Birthday   | june     | march | july       | august |

